text: hello what brings you in today
Hey. Just feeling worn out all the time and my legs are swelling up. That's about it.
when did this begin
It's been going on for a while now. Hard to say exactly when it started, but it's gotten worse lately.
how's your breathing been
I get short of breath when I walk too far or climb stairs.
are you having any chest pain
No, I haven't had any chest pain.
are you having any pain
I've got this deep ache in my bones, like I've been hauling pipe all day.
have you had any trauma
No, I haven't had any trauma recently.
any fever
Nope, no fever that I've noticed.
how long have you been having pain in your bones
It's been a while now. Hard to pinpoint exactly, but it's been getting worse as time goes on.
do you have any cough
No, I haven't had a cough.
anything makes it better
Not really. Rest helps a bit, but the tiredness and aches don't go away completely.
anything makes it worse
oving around too much seems to make the swelling and tiredness worse.
is a swelling worse in the morning
No, it seems to get worse as the day goes on.
where's the swelling located in your body
y legs swell up pretty bad, sometimes it goes up past my knees.
what would you rate your pain out of 10
I'd say it's around a 5 or 6 most days. It's more of a constant ache than sharp pain.
has this ever happened to you before
Not like this. I've had aches and pains from work, but nothing that sticks around like this.
do you have any numbness or tingling
Yeah, my fingers and toes tingle or go numb sometimes, especially when I'm driving.
do you have any twitching
I'm sorry, I had trouble understanding you. Could you please rephrase that?
are you having any muscles spasms or muscle cramps
I'm sorry, I had trouble understanding you. Could you please rephrase that?
have you had any weight loss
Yeah, I've dropped some weight without trying. Food just doesn't sit right anymore.
how much weight
I'm not really sure of the exact amount, but I've definitely noticed my clothes feeling a bit looser lately.
do you have lots of appetite
Not really. Food doesn't sit right, and everything tastes like metal, so I don't eat much.
do you have any nausea or vomiting
Yeah, I feel like throwing up most days.
have you vomit
Yeah, I've vomited a few times lately.
is there blood in your vomit
No, I haven't noticed any blood in it.
any changes in your urinary habits
I pee less than I used to, and sometimes it's darker, but I figured I just wasn't drinking enough.
how much are you drinking
I try to drink water throughout the day, but I guess not as much as I should. I usually have coffee in the morning too.
have you noticed any palpitations or racing heartbeat
No, I haven't noticed any palpitations or a racing heartbeat.
give me diarrhea or constipation
I don't really know. I haven't noticed any diarrhea.
what about constipation
I haven't really noticed any issues with that.
is there blood in your urine
No, I haven't noticed any blood in my urine.
tell me about your exercise habits
I used to be pretty active with my plumbing work, but lately, I haven't been able to do much. I try to move around a bit at home, but I get tired quickly.
do you have any known exposure to lead pipes
Not sure what that means. I work with pipes a lot, but I haven't really thought about lead.
do you have any hazardous material exposure
Not that I know of. I mostly work with plumbing materials, nothing too hazardous as far as I can tell.
what is your past medical history
I've had high blood pressure since my thirties and had a mild stroke a while back, but I got better from that. I've also been in the hospital for lung congestion before.
do you smoke
No, I never smoked.
are you having any trouble swallowing
No, I haven't had any trouble with swallowing.
what medications do you take
I've got a whole bunch of medicines I'm on that I can't pronounce. My girlfriend makes me keep a list in my wallet.
can I have it
Sure, the list includes potassium chloride, clonidine patch, clopidogrel, atenolol, iron, and aspirin.
why are you taking the iron
I'm not really sure. You'd have to ask the doctors about that.
do you have any drug allergies
None that I know of.
can tell me more about your stroke when you were in the hospital in any complications that you're having
I had a mild stroke a while back, which caused temporary weakness on my left side, but I got better. I haven't had any complications from it since then.
have you noticed any sores in the mouth or bleeding in the mouth
No, I haven't noticed any sores or bleeding in my mouth.
have you noticed any painful urination or urinary frequency
No, I haven't noticed any pain or changes like that when I go to the bathroom.
are you having a dry mouth
Yeah, my mouth does feel dry sometimes.
how's your oral hygiene
I try to keep up with it, but my breath still smells bad, like fish, even after brushing.
have you noticed any headache or changes in your vision
Bright lights bother me, and my girlfriend says my eyes look puffy and bulging. I haven't really had headaches, though.
what is your family medical history
y dad died young at 45 from high blood pressure and diabetes. My mom had breast cancer and passed away at 60.
have you been sick recently
No, I haven't been sick recently, just dealing with these ongoing issues.
have you noticed any rash or itching
Yeah, my skin itches when my legs are swollen.
have you had any trouble walking
Yeah, I've been having some trouble walking. My legs swell up pretty bad, and I get tired quickly, so it's been tough to move around like I used to.
any trouble with your balance
I get dizzy if I stand up too fast, but I haven't really noticed any major balance issues.
